# Drop common Pokémon GO icons here, named <token>.png, referenced in event text
# as :token: (e.g. :stardust: -> assets/icons/stardust.png). Missing files hide
# gracefully. IMPORTANT: git-commit any icons you add — run-daily.sh's rollback
# runs `git clean -fdq public`, which deletes untracked files under public/.
#
# Suggested tokens: stardust candy candy-xl xp incense lure megaenergy ticket
# pokeball greatball ultraball luckyegg starpiece raidpass remoteraidpass
